owdragon/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fzzang_cowdragon%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=a676cf8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/zzang_cowdragon/</a><br />\n哲宗IG:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/iron_bell_2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Firon_bell_2%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=698f48cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/iron_bell_2/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.viu.com/ott/hk/zh-hk/vod/317465/%E5%93%B2%E4%BB%81%E7%8E%8B%E5%90%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viu.com%2Fott%2Fhk%2Fzh-hk%2Fvod%2F317465%2F%25E5%2593%25B2%25E4%25BB%2581%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2590%258E&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=d3c4b1ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.viu.com/ott/hk/zh-hk/vod/317465/%E5%93%B2%E4%BB%81%E7%8E%8B%E5%90%8E</a> VIU 哲仁王后-1-20集<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.viu.com/ott/hk/zh-hk/vod/336230/%E5%93%B2%E4%BB%81%E7%8E%8B%E5%90%8E-The-Secret\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viu.com%2Fott%2Fhk%2Fzh-hk%2Fvod%2F336230%2F%25E5%2593%25B2%25E4%25BB%2581%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2590%258E-The-Secret&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=547850de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.viu.com/ott/hk/zh-hk/vod/336230/%E5%93%B2%E4%BB%81%E7%8E%8B%E5%90%8E-The-Secret</a> VIU 哲仁王后番外-竹林篇(1-2集)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.viu.com/ott/hk/zh-hk/vod/342218/%E5%93%B2%E4%BB%81%E7%8E%8B%E5%90%8E-%E6%97%A5%E8%AB%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viu.com%2Fott%2Fhk%2Fzh-hk%2Fvod%2F342218%2F%25E5%2593%25B2%25E4%25BB%2581%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2590%258E-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25AB%2587&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=b3e29e82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.viu.com/ott/hk/zh-hk/vod/342218/%E5%93%B2%E4%BB%81%E7%8E%8B%E5%90%8E-%E6%97%A5%E8%AB%87</a>  哲仁王后：日談 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc5pG9WGEnHef1FMKAqLDhi6qzM9Qwr5nirvYzzLdyjwm?filename=K2k0Jx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2k0Jx4.jpg&h=8ed40899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被張奉煥的靈魂附身的朝鮮王妃（尊稱中殿）。昭容為了家族、也為了不讓生下她後去世的母親白白死去，也為了對父親盡孝，將「被揀擇成為中殿」視為存在的理由，竭盡全力的生活。但進宮後發現哲宗身邊已經有花真了，自己什麼也做不了。能夠敞開心扉的只有崔尚宮和洪燕而已，因此性格變得孤僻，成為了後宮們口中的「別宮魔女」。其實昭容一開始和哲宗見面的時候就被哲宗迷住了，心想：「這不是為了家族而有的政治婚姻，而是有愛情的婚姻。」但不久後，在命運的驅使下，沉浸在無法擺脫的絕望裡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUw3B6Hw6uJhSQnvu9aG2ye2Di7BritVFE3xcgHtFNZBS?filename=UpYJGjU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpYJGjU.jpg&h=713aa61b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝鮮國王（尊稱主上），本名李元範。永平君的異母弟弟。從表面上看是個文雅懦弱的傀儡王，但隱藏著很多秘密。人們嘲笑哲宗是為了不像家人一樣被殺才自願成為傀儡，但實際上他最害怕的是：按照那些人的願望，他成為了一個無能的國王，什麼都無法做就死去。隱藏著夢想的哲宗，暗地裡規劃他的改革夢，是個面對不斷阻擋自己的命運，也不輕易屈服的堅強的複合型人物，具備著雙面的性格。<br />\n<br />\n幕後花絮:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HuwcXBpPuks&amp;list=PLrVl5v_HQFa3w436nDZFOxbniez5rNVnd&amp;index=48 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHuwcXBpPuks%26list%3DPLrVl5v_HQFa3w436nDZFOxbniez5rNVnd%26index%3D48%20&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=13f94315\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HuwcXBpPuks&amp;list=PLrVl5v_HQFa3w436nDZFOxbniez5rNVnd&amp;index=48 </a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2344601/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2344601/page/1</a> [viu]韓劇 哲仁王后 (1)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2366026/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2366026/page/1</a> [viu]韓劇 哲仁王后 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2382534/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2382534/page/1</a> [viu]韓劇 哲仁王后 (3) - 星期六一齊食拉麵啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2393288/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2393288/page/1</a> [viu]韓劇 哲仁王后 (4) - 賀喜主上MAMA 一索(ONE SHOT) 得子<br />